         <abstract><p>The homily on Melchizedek's origin attributed to <persName ref="PRS3255CyrilI"/>, mainly circulate as part of the theological collection 'Qərəllos'. It was certainly translated from the Greek: the original is lost and the Ethiopic version is the only existing one. 
         </p>
